20/06/2003
WASHINGTON, United States -- Secretary of State Colin Powell has formally invited Turkish Foreign Minister Abdullah Gul to Washington, according to Foreign Ministry Undersecretary Ugur Ziyal, who is currently visiting the United States.
Ziyal added that a visit by Prime Minister Recep Tayyip Erdogan would also be discussed, though no dates have been announced.
(Anadolu Agency, TRT 2 - 19/06/03)
